# Testing Conventions

## Structure
describe('<METHOD> <route>', () => {
  it('should <expected behavior>', async () => { ... })
})

## Integration tests
Use supertest with the Express app from src/app.ts.
Each test file imports { app } from '../../src/app'.
Use beforeAll/afterAll for DB setup and teardown.
Never use real production DB — use the taskflow_test database.

## What to test
Every route: happy path, 400 bad input, 404 not found, 500 error.
Every service: unit test with mocked DB pool.

## Assertions
Use expect(res.status).toBe(xxx) before asserting body.
Always assert res.body.success and res.body.data shape.
